;The Mozilla Leadership Network
Le rete de leadership de Mozilla


;Connecting Leaders
Connecter le leaders


;The Mozilla Leadership Network is a global network of diverse leaders - from the young activist teaching web literacy to her community, to the executive leading a global organization - who will ensure the next wave of access, inclusion and opportunity online.
Le rete de commando de Mozilla es un rete global de diverse strategos - ab le juvene activista qui insenia alphabetisation del web a su communitate, al executive qui duce un organisation global - qui assecurara le proxime unda de accesso, inclusion e opportunitate a internet.


;Leaders in this network will take action together to:
Le strategos in iste rete se activara insimul pro:


;Shape and spread the open internet agenda;
Formar e diffunder le agenda de internet aperte;


;Model ‘open’ values and practices in institutions, products and policies around the world.
Promover valores e practicas ‘aperte’ in institutiones, productos e politicas circum le mundo.


;How we work
Como nos labora


;The Mozilla Leadership Network accomplishes its work through thematic ‘hubs,’ communities of people with diverse expertise, who are helping others build the capacity to advance the open Internet in their field or topic of interest.
Le Rete de commando de Mozilla compli su labor per ‘centros’ thematic, communitates de personas con diverse competentia, qui adjuta alteres a construer le capacitate pro facer progreder internet aperte in lor campo o topico de interesse.


;Our current hubs include:
Nostre centros actual include:


;<a href="%(url_learning)s">Learning.</a> Educators and librarians committed to transforming learning in our digital age.
<a href="%(url_learning)s">Apprender.</a> Educatores e librerias ingagiate a transformar le apprendimento in nostre era digital.


;<a href="%(url_science)s">Science.</a> Researchers and data scientists committed to making research and practice more open.
<a href="%(url_science)s">Scientia.</a> Recercatores e scientistas de datos ingagiate a render le recerca e le practica plus aperte.


;<a href="%(url_advocacy)s">Internet Policy & Advocacy.</a> Individuals and organizations focused on advancing open Internet issues.
<a href="%(url_advocacy)s">Politica & defensa de internet.</a> Individuos e organisationes focalisate pro avantiar le progresso del problemas internet aperte.


;<a href="%(url_women)s">Women & Web Literacy.</a> Community organizers and senior leaders creating opportunities for women and girls to develop web literacy skills.
<a href="%(url_women)s">Le feminas e le alphabetisation web.</a> Organisatores e senior strategos del communitate crea opportunitates pro feminas e pueras pro disveloppar le habilitates de alphabetisation del web.


;<a href="%(url_iot)s">Internet of Things.</a> Hackers and designers creating provocative prototypes for what an open Internet of Things could and should be.
<a href="%(url_iot)s">Internet del cosas.</a> Hackers e ingenieros que crea provocative prototypos pro lo que un internet aperte del cosas poterea e deberea ser.


;Our Initiatives
Nostre initiativas


;The Mozilla Leadership Network pursues our goals through five key initiatives, which are reflected in each hub:
Le Rete de commando de Mozilla perseque nostre scopos per cinque initiativas clave, que es reflectite in cata centro:


;<em>Curricula & Training.</em> We provide free and open curricula and training programs to help leaders develop the skills they need to ensure the next wave of access, inclusion and opportunity online. Example: <a href="%(url_weblit_module)s">Web Literacy Training Module</a>
<em>Curricula & Training.</em> Nos forni curricula libere e aperte e programmas de training pro adjutar le strategos a disveloppar le habilitates que illos besonia pro assecurar le proxime unda de accesso, inclusion e opportunitate online. Exemplo: <a href="%(url_weblit_module)s">Modulo de training de alphabetisation del web</a>


;<em>Partnerships.</em> We initiate and grow partnerships that enable Mozilla, our community and our allies to maximize their impact. Example: <a href="%(url_gigabit)s">Gigabit Community Fund</a>
<em>Association.</em> Nos initia e accresce le association que activa Mozilla, nostre communitate e nostre alliatos a maximisar lor impacto. Exemplo: <a href="%(url_gigabit)s">Fundar le Communitate Gigabit</a>


;<em>Convening.</em> We bring members of the Mozilla Leadership Network together, to learn from one another, exchange ideas and join forces. Example: <a href="%(url_mozFest)s">MozFest</a>
<em>Convening.</em> Nos reuni le membros del Rete de commando de Mozilla, pro apprender le un le alteres, excambiar ideas e junger le fortias. Exemplo: <a href="%(url_mozFest)s">MozFest</a>


;<em>Membership.</em> Members join because they share Mozilla’s vision, and stay because of the strong, diverse community and unique professional development opportunities the network provides. Example: <a href="%(url_fellowships)s">Fellowships</a>
<em>Membros.</em> Le membros se junge perque illes comparti le vision de Mozilla, e resta per le forte, diverse communitate e unic opportunitates de disveloppamento professional que le rete forni. Exemplo: <a href="%(url_fellowships)s">Associationes</a>


